  "title": "Chyma",
  "description": "Adds a CustomHud variable for whether the minimap is currently shown on the hud",
  "body": "## Chyma\n\n### Chyma for 1.21.1 requires [CustomHud](https://modrinth.com/mod/customhud) v4 and [JourneyMap](https://modrinth.com/mod/journeymap) API v2 (found in Journeymap beta 6.0 and up). \nSpecifically, it requires `customhud >=4.0.0-` and `journeymap >=1.21-6.0.0-`\n\n\n**Chyma adds the boolean variables** `jm` **and** `jm_minimap` **to CustomHud. Their value is whether the ingame minimap (not fullscreen map) is currently displayed on your hud.**\n\n\n\n![janky screenshot showing minimap enabled or disabled, side by side comparison](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/35e4edc08dbcd8c0d0e5ef3c890a966c841397c7.png)\n*- CHJMA: Acronym for \"CustomHud JourneyMap Addon\"  (pronounced 'chime-uh')*  \n*- Chyma: The above, but easier to read and pronounce*\n\n<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>